OL,3,CRNLI rescues two people after plane
OL,4,Ccrashes into sea off Ceredigion coast
OL,6,FRNLI lifeboat crews from West Wales
OL,7,Fand a rescue helicopter responded to a
OL,8,Fmajor emergency on Friday (26 June)
OL,9,Fafter a light aircraft carrying two
OL,10,Fpeople crashed into the sea off the
OL,11,FCeredigion coast.
OL,13,FThe plane was travelling from Ireland
OL,14,Fto Aberporth, where it was due to stop
OL,15,Fovernight and refuel before continuing
OL,16,Fits journey to Italy.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
