OL,3,CRNLI rescues two people after plane
OL,4,Ccrashes into sea off Ceredigion coast
OL,6,FTwo aircrafts were travelling together
OL,7,Fwhen one experienced mechanical
OL,8,Fdifficulties, prompting a emergency
OL,9,Fcall to HM Coastguard before it was
OL,10,Fforced to crash into the sea.
OL,12,FRNLI crews from New Quay, Cardigan and
OL,13,FFishguard and a HM Coastguard
OL,14,Fhelicopter arrived on the scene where
OL,15,Fthe plane had crashed 10 miles north-
OL,16,Fwest of Cemaes Head, near Cardigan.
OL,18,FTwo people were taken to hospital
OL,19,Fbefore being discharged on Saturday
OL,20,F(27 June).
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
