OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782686872
OL,3,CRNLI rescues two people after plane
OL,4,Ccrashes into sea off Ceredigion coast
OL,6,FBernie Davies, New Quay RNLI's
OL,7,FCoxswain, said:
OL,9,F"RNLI Cardigan's Atlantic 85 launched
OL,10,Fand was first on scene with the
OL,11,FCoastguard helicopter. The aircraft
OL,12,Fwreckage was quickly located, floating
OL,13,Fin the water with both casualties
OL,14,Fsitting on top, wearing lifejackets.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
