FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782686872
OL,3,CRNLI rescues two people after plane
OL,4,Ccrashes into sea off Ceredigion coast
OL,6,F"The Cardigan crew brought the
OL,7,Flifeboat alongside and safely
OL,8,Frecovered both individuals on board.
OL,9,FThe casualties were found to be
OL,10,Fextremely cold but conscious and
OL,11,Fresponsive. Crew provided immediate
OL,12,Fcasualty care.
OL,14,F"When we arrived shortly afterwards,
OL,15,FRNLI Cardigan transferred of both
OL,16,Fcasualties to our lifeboat, where they
OL,17,Freceived further treatment, including
OL,18,Fhot drinks and ongoing casualty care.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
