OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782686872
OL,3,CRNLI rescues two people after plane
OL,4,Ccrashes into sea off Ceredigion coast
OL,6,F"We then transported the casualties to
OL,7,FNew Quay harbour, where they were
OL,8,Fbrought ashore at the main pier and
OL,9,Fhanded into the care of the Welsh
OL,10,FAmbulance Service before being
OL,11,Ftransferred to hospital."
OL,13,FRees-Tom Jones, New Quay RNLI's
OL,14,Fnavigator, said:
OL,16,F"The casualties were in shock and
OL,17,Fspent one night in hospital before
OL,18,Fbeing discharged yesterday (Saturday)
OL,19,Fand have since taken the ferry back to
OL,20,FIreland from Fishguard."
